  }, "v25"), mdx("p", null, "Ban \u0111\xEAm c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111i theo Sau-l\u01A1 gi\xFAp \xF4ng tho\xE1t b\u1EB1ng c\xE1ch cho \xF4ng ng\u1ED3i trong th\xFAng r\u1ED3i th\xF2ng \xF4ng xu\u1ED1ng qua m\u1ED9t l\u1ED7 h\u1ED5ng trong v\xE1ch th\xE0nh.Sau-l\u01A1 gi\u1EA3ng t\u1EA1i Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v26"
  }, "v26"), mdx("p", null, "Khi Sau-l\u01A1 tr\u1EDF v\u1EC1 Gi\xEA-ru-sa-lem, th\xEC \xF4ng t\xECm c\xE1ch gia nh\u1EADp nh\xF3m c\xE1c t\xEDn h\u1EEFu nh\u01B0ng ai c\u0169ng e ng\u1EA1i. Kh\xF4ng ai tin \xF4ng ta l\xE0 t\xEDn h\u1EEFu th\u1EADt. "), mdx("h6", {
