  }, "v37"), mdx("p", null, "Trong khi Phia-r\u01A1 \u1EDF L\xFD-\u0111a th\xEC Ta-bi-tha b\u1ECB b\u1EC7nh v\xE0 qua \u0111\u1EDDi. Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi ra t\u1EAFm x\xE1c ch\u1ECB v\xE0 \u0111\u1EB7t n\u1EB1m trong m\u1ED9t ph\xF2ng tr\xEAn g\xE1c. "), mdx("h6", {
